{"tid":1133151,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[熱狗］普捷天奴：活在夢裡","createTime":"2019-04-30T20:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T21:06:31.000Z","uid":11258,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd287951b7f6bb2f8ddd239bcb07ceb5a35cadd","tid":1133151,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T20:57:37.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】熱刺在周二歐聯4強首回合主場迎戰阿積士力爭球會史上首次殺入決賽，領隊普捷天奴坦言活在夢裡。<br />\n<br />\n「我正活在夢裡。其實我已經歷過，5年前帶領熱刺出戰4強就是一個美夢。當你發夢的時候，一定要遠大一點，要無盡甚至超越無盡。」普捷天奴（Mauricio Pochettino）在賽前記者會上說。<br />\n<br />\n加盟熱刺5年來，至今仍然未嚐冠軍滋味，普帥表示：「若你問我怎樣把球會帶到另一層次，像皇家馬德里及巴塞隆拿那樣，贏得一個冠軍並不足夠，需要成為歐聯及英超的爭標份子。」<br />\n<br />\n射手哈利卡尼正在養傷，普捷天奴坦言他沒有可能在次回合復出：「他的情況很好，已經可以開始跑步。不過，我們不可以創造任何不能達成的目標，最重要是他進度良好，之後看看情況如何。」<br />\n<br />\n熱刺VS阿積士<br />\nNow TV 643台01/05 03:00直播<br />\nNow E 同步直播<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恭喜普sir今晚繼續發個好夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ca4aea60eac140354df1ed46a676d7b147e277","tid":1133151,"uid":11258,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T21:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JGyWJvs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGyWJvs.gif&h=af84478e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eef91ac872e5eefeddbf7d04b0b932adcc95a19","tid":1133151,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T06:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s1mUyma.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs1mUyma.gif&h=74a8e3a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34a447d33be8476a6cbe4013282ccd137fa846db","tid":1133151,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T06:43:49.000Z","msg":"夢醒啦"},{"pid":"a051b68db10f17ae33555bc4510ab15204c11e1b","tid":1133151,"uid":17842,"like":0,"dislike":0